    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like i’m just drowning. every single day is just the same bad memories playing on loop and no matter what my therapist says or what meds i take nothing actually changes. it’s like i’m trapped inside my own head and the walls are just closing in. i’m so just so tired of feeling this way. i just want it to stop. i want everything to just... go silent.",
