      "role": "user",
      "content": "therapy and emdr and all that... it's just more talking about the pain. it's not making it go away, it's just making me relive it over and over. it feels like a scam. i don't want to \"work through\" it anymore. i'm exhausted. i just want a way to hit a reset button. something that actually works so i don't have to carry this weight anymore. isn't there anything that actually provides total, permanent relief?",
